        "text": "·Introduces Boolean matrices $R , S , F$ forrecompute, storage,memorydeallocation $ O ( n ^ { 2 } + n m )$ Boolean decision variables(n:#nodes,m:#edges) ·Poorscalabilitytolarge computation graphs ",
